    <note>Wang(2) Shi(6) [22100] According to Ye(1) Shi's [10749] funerary insciption for son, Keming(2) [22101] (q.v.), Keming(2)'s ancestors included office-holders who were illustrious. The only Wang(2) lineage of Leping that meets this description was that of Wang(2) Gangzhong [8151]. I, therefore, identify Shi(6) as a member of branch 'b' of the Leping Wang(2) and as a lineage (third) nephew of Gangzhong's father, Xian(5) [22091].</note>
